title: You haven't changed a bit
creator_credit: Karl Holtsnider, Teleketics and Bruce Baker
brief_description: A dramatization about a young couple who after a quarrel take separate vacations at their respective parents’ homes. In the process they discover that despite their past associations their real identity lies in their relationship with each other.
